text: Nechervan Idris Barzani (Kurdish:نێچیرڤان بارزانی, Nêçîrvan Îdrîs Barzanî) (born 21 September 1966) has been the Prime Minister of Iraqi Kurdistan since March 2006. Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Iraqi politicians Category:Kurdish politicians Category:Prime ministers
title: Nechervan Idris Barzani
